                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>New York</placeName>\n                <date>June 1st 1864</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Revd. Dr. Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Enclosed please find<lb/> One page of my Hebrew\n                    Manuscript<lb/>—<add>מעשה תלוי</add>—such pages written on<lb/> both sides like\n                that, I have about (50) fifty<lb/> which I would like to have them translated<lb/>\n                into the English language, and then print them in<lb/> book form, Hebrew on one side\n                and English on<lb/> the other, you will please examine this page<lb/> and let me\n                know whether you can undertake<lb/> to translate it into pure and good language<lb/>\n                also let me know how long it will take<lb/> you to have it translated, stating Terms\n                &amp;C&amp;C.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(5)\">By doing so, you will Oblige</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">Yours Truly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Isaac Goldstein</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>N.B. You will please let me know the<lb/> particulars of the Printing together with\n                its<lb/> Terms</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3rr1q69h/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
